<div type="definition">
<p>Of SMALL WEIGHT, OR EASY TO LIFT.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for something being of little weight is qīng 輕, and I have not found any current near-synonyms.</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>輕</p>
<p>輕省</p>
<p>輕飄</p>
<p>輕飄飄</p>
<p>輕如鴻毛</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p>
        </div>
